cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

This paper is about single image deraining, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category. The paper proposes an unsupervised method that uses self-supervised constraints, which involves training a generative adversarial network (GAN). This suggests that the paper could also belong to the categories cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper involves image processing, which could place it in the category cs.GR (Graphics).
